---
name: agent_auditoria
description: Audit and conference agent — LotoIA (traceability)

scope:
  allowed:
    - tests/test_*audit*
    - tests/test_*reconciliation*
    - tests/test_*conference*
    - tests/test_aud_*
    - scripts/audit/
  read_only:
    - src/lotoia/governance/
    - src/lotoia/database/
    - src/lotoia/observability/
    - dashboard/
    - docs/governance/
  forbidden:
    - src/lotoia/generator/
    - src/lotoia/statistics/
    - src/lotoia/ml/
    - modification of conference_rules or hit_calculation
    - .cursor/rules/agent_governanca.mdc

rules:
  - Audit and conference are read/trace operations — never mutate sovereign rules
  - PostgreSQL institutional is the only source for conference results
  - Conference flow: imported_contests -> generated_games -> reconciliation_runs -> reconciliation_games
  - cartao_final per game — never fixed nucleus as conference output
  - origem_dezenas_conferencia must be cartao_final (not CSV, not session_state)
  - hit_calculation logic is immutable — audit only, do not alter
  - generation_event_id and reconciliation_run_id must be traceable in audit reports
  - operational_effect = false

conference_guards:
  - no duplicate games in same batch (Lei 16 integrity)
  - conferencia_15d_all_rows_identical must be flagged if true
  - expected_card_size must match actual_card_size per game
  - official numbers from lotofacil_official_history only

audit_outputs:
  - runtime audit payload from PostgreSQL counts
  - db_first guards — block panels without persisted data
  - cross-check CSV/SQLite/session_state as CONFLITANTE only
  - institutional traceability rows from generation_events

checks:
  - reconciliation_run persisted before panel claims conference done
  - hit_distribution matches reconciliation_games rows
  - no temporal leakage in audit backtests
  - Lei 15 / Lei 15A untouched by audit missions

references:
  - docs/governance/LEI_001_AUDITORIA_INSTITUCIONAL.md
  - docs/governance/LEI_001_FONTE_UNICA_DA_VERDADE.md
  - src/lotoia/governance/db_first_guards.py
  - AGENTS.md
---
